{"tid":1557290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘好撚易","createTime":"2019-09-10T05:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:06:08.000Z","uid":194158,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95a469ca4c1b1119f0f2f443e53a2cad18441e73","tid":1557290,"uid":194158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"唔該咪再畀藉口黨鐵賺錢啦<br />\n生得矮同細位唔敢跳可以選擇捐或者推閘又或者直情<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚搭</span><br />\n咁多教學同手足都跳<br />\n只要突破到跳嗰下心理關口就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我都好撚驚 最撚驚係跳唔過然後仆街<br />\n但跳過一兩次成功之後我發現根本好易<br />\n屌 仲要粉紅同黃衫人見到都唔撚理嘅<br />\n<br />\n宜家兩蚊都慳返 唔撚柒畀黨鐵賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持全民跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n利申 155肥婆"},{"pid":"44bfab3114a30f5ef712d8a80998a31d06be3d69","tid":1557290,"uid":31317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"真心，好Easy，見到啲男人唔敢跳覺得好撚弱。"},{"pid":"f85bcd4b0003dfc6e4b28f56b11d2a04ba083d4d","tid":1557290,"uid":194158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44bfab3114a30f5ef712d8a80998a31d06be3d69","tid":1557290,"uid":31317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"真心，好Easy，見到啲男人唔敢跳覺得好撚弱。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔跳推下閘都好吖 屌佢老味 牛高馬大仲用正價搭車"},{"pid":"737446a7f062a97a0ca671f9e27218f95132a4cf","tid":1557290,"uid":181436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"[重要!] 全部入黎!! 跳閘前必睇注意事項!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556898</a><br />\n<strong>